Read cbop data and adjust the defition of units

cbop_2018_1 %>%
  count(przez_prac, kod_rodz_zatrud) %>%
  group_by(przez_prac) %>%
  mutate(p  = n/sum(n)*100)

cbop_2018_1 %>%
  count(kod_rodz_zatrud) %>%
  mutate(p  = n/sum(n)*100)
